	should be truncated (Ron).

	* libtiff/{tif_dirinfo.c, tif_config.h.vc}: Use lfind() instead
	of bsearch() in _TIFFFindFieldInfoByName() function (Ron).

	* libtiff/{tiff.h, tif_dirinfo.c}: Fixes in EXIF tag ordering (Ron).

